<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Kalmirth — Explore the World</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;600;700&family=Crimson+Pro:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300;1,400&display=swap');

  :root {
    --gold: #C89B3C;
    --gold-dim: #8a6a28;
    --gold-glow: rgba(200,155,60,0.15);
    --bg: #080b14;
    --card: #0d1220;
    --card-hover: #111826;
    --text: #d4be8a;
    --text-dim: #7a6a4a;
    --border: rgba(200,155,60,0.18);
    --border-hover: rgba(200,155,60,0.5);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', Georgia, serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* Background image */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url('../game-bg/hub-banner.jpeg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center 40%;
    opacity: 0.18;
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    filter: saturate(0.5) blur(0.5px);
  }

  /* Mist overlay */
  body::after {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 100%, rgba(8,11,20,0.85) 0%, transparent 55%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 0% 50%, rgba(8,11,20,0.5) 0%, transparent 45%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 100% 50%, rgba(8,11,20,0.5) 0%, transparent 45%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(8,11,20,0.5) 0%, transparent 25%, transparent 75%, rgba(8,11,20,0.7) 100%);
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .page-wrap {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 900px;
    padding: 60px 24px 80px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 60px;
  }

  /* Header */
  header {
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .continent-label {
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--gold-dim);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.2s forwards;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.4s forwards;
  }

  .divider {
    width: 120px;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.6s forwards;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    max-width: 440px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.7s forwards;
  }

  /* Game grid */
  .game-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .game-card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 2px;
    padding: 32px 28px 28px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease var(--delay) forwards;
  }

  .game-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at top left, var(--gold-glow), transparent 60%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.4s;
  }

  .game-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
    background: var(--card-hover);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  .game-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }

  .card-icon {
    font-size: 28px;
    line-height: 1;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .card-location {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.35em;
    color: var(--gold-dim);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .card-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .card-desc {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .card-cta {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .game-card:hover .card-cta { opacity: 1; }

  /* Separator line inside card */
  .card-line {
    width: 40px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    transition: width 0.3s, background 0.3s;
  }

  .game-card:hover .card-line {
    width: 60px;
    background: var(--gold-dim);
  }

  /* Footer */
  footer {
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 1.2s forwards;
  }

  .back-link {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .back-link:hover { color: var(--gold); }

  .back-link::before {
    content: '←';
    font-family: serif;
  }

  .footer-note {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page-wrap">
  <header>
    <div class="continent-label">Night Etdler · Continent of Kalmirth</div>
    <h1>Explore the World</h1>
    <div class="divider"></div>
    <p class="tagline">These are not stories about wars or chosen ones. These are the hours between.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="game-grid">
    <a class="game-card" href="blue-river/index.html" style="--delay: 0.8s">
      <div class="card-icon">🎣</div>
      <div class="card-location">The Blue River</div>
      <div class="card-title">A Day on the River</div>
      <div class="card-line"></div>
      <p class="card-desc">Cast your line. Wait. The river doesn't care who you are or what faction you belong to.</p>
      <div class="card-cta">Enter →</div>
    </a>

    <a class="game-card" href="bronzefinger/index.html" style="--delay: 0.95s">
      <div class="card-icon">🔨</div>
      <div class="card-location">Bronzefinger's Forge</div>
      <div class="card-title">A Day at the Forge</div>
      <div class="card-line"></div>
      <p class="card-desc">Run the shop for a day. Do good work. Get paid in increasingly creative ways.</p>
      <div class="card-cta">Enter →</div>
    </a>

    <a class="game-card" href="walking-sim/index.html" style="--delay: 1.1s">
      <div class="card-icon">🚶</div>
      <div class="card-location">Blue River Village</div>
      <div class="card-title">A Walk Through Town</div>
      <div class="card-line"></div>
      <p class="card-desc">You're passing through. Nobody knows your name. The village is alive without you.</p>
      <div class="card-cta">Enter →</div>
    </a>

    <a class="game-card" href="night-origins/index.html" style="--delay: 1.1s">
      <div class="card-icon">◈</div>
      <div class="card-location">Blue River Village · The Beginning</div>
      <div class="card-title">Night Origins</div>
      <div class="card-line"></div>
      <p class="card-desc">Seven chapters. The crystal that started everything. The last ordinary night. The assault that broke it all. Start here — continue in The First Night.</p>
      <div class="card-cta">Enter →</div>
    </a>

    <a class="game-card" href="vleyrra/index.html" style="--delay: 1.25s">
      <div class="card-icon">✦</div>
      <div class="card-location">Vleyrra Forest · Kingdom of the Blinding Light</div>
      <div class="card-title">The First Night</div>
      <div class="card-line"></div>
      <p class="card-desc">Avery fled the Black Leaf attack alone. Two days lost in Vleyrra. Then a boy with a bow made of light shot something off her face and said sorry. This is how she found the kingdom the Mage Hunters could never find.</p>
      <div class="card-cta">Enter →</div>
    </a>

    <a class="game-card" href="deepborn-siege/index.html" style="--delay: 1.4s">
      <div class="card-icon">⚔️</div>
      <div class="card-location">Night Crystal Alliance · Tower Defense</div>
      <div class="card-title">Deepborn Siege</div>
      <div class="card-line"></div>
      <p class="card-desc">Defend the Alliance base from the Deepborn Horde. Place towers. Hold the line. 20 waves of increasing danger.</p>
      <div class="card-cta">Enter →</div>
    </a>

    <a class="game-card" href="theas-stand/index.html" style="--delay: 1.55s">
      <div class="card-icon">🗡️</div>
      <div class="card-location">Nordell Border Forces · Hack & Slash</div>
      <div class="card-title">Thea's Stand</div>
      <div class="card-line"></div>
      <p class="card-desc">Commander of Nordell Border forces. Twenty years fighting the Deepborn with nothing but steel. No magic. No backup. Just you and the dark.</p>
      <div class="card-cta">Enter →</div>
    </a>

    <a class="game-card" href="callens-training/index.html" style="--delay: 1.7s">
      <div class="card-icon">⚔️</div>
      <div class="card-location">Aysel Village · Beat 'Em Up</div>
      <div class="card-title">Callen's Training</div>
      <div class="card-line"></div>
      <p class="card-desc">Two years after the assault. You train under the man who led the attack on Blue River Village. He doesn't tell you. Not yet.</p>
      <div class="card-cta">Enter →</div>
    </a>

    <a class="game-card" href="averys-children/index.html" style="--delay: 1.85s">
      <div class="card-icon">💎</div>
      <div class="card-location">Alliance Base · Co-op Platformer</div>
      <div class="card-title">Avery's Children</div>
      <div class="card-line"></div>
      <p class="card-desc">Lucas, Sheriel, and Afriel — three siblings with crystal powers. Work together to explore the ancient ruins.</p>
      <div class="card-cta">Enter →</div>
    </a>

    <a class="game-card" href="mythanar/index.html" style="--delay: 2.0s">
      <div class="card-icon">🕳️</div>
      <div class="card-location">Blue River Village · The Cave</div>
      <div class="card-title">Mythanar's Cave</div>
      <div class="card-line"></div>
      <p class="card-desc">The ancient elven challenge. Five plates. A cage. A mannequin. The cave is asking something. What will you refuse?</p>
      <div class="card-cta">Enter →</div>
    </a>

    <a class="game-card" href="../Idle/qwen-version/game.html" style="--delay: 1.85s">
      <div class="card-icon">🪙</div>
      <div class="card-location">Night Crystal Alliance · Idle RPG</div>
      <div class="card-title">Echoes of the First Breach</div>
      <div class="card-line"></div>
      <p class="card-desc">An idle RPG with a real ending. Tap to fight Deepborn, hire faction heroes, make Commander decisions that shape the story.</p>
      <div class="card-cta">Enter →</div>
    </a>

    <a class="game-card" href="../Idle/qwen-version-td/game.html" style="--delay: 2.0s">
      <div class="card-icon">🏰</div>
      <div class="card-location">Underworld Breach · Tower Defense</div>
      <div class="card-title">The First Breach</div>
      <div class="card-line"></div>
      <p class="card-desc">Place faction towers along the Deepborn breach path. Five factions, synergies, Commander abilities. Hold the line through 30 waves.</p>
      <div class="card-cta">Enter →</div>
    </a>

    <a class="game-card" href="../Idle/qwen-version-hns/game.html" style="--delay: 2.15s">
      <div class="card-icon">⚔️</div>
      <div class="card-location">Nordell Border · Hack & Slash</div>
      <div class="card-title">The Commander's Blade</div>
      <div class="card-line"></div>
      <p class="card-desc">Play as Thea, Avery, Nate, or Fran. Light and heavy combos, dodge rolls, character-unique specials. 15 waves of Deepborn with boss fights.</p>
      <div class="card-cta">Enter →</div>
    </a>

    <a class="game-card" href="callen-training/index.html" style="--delay: 2.3s">
      <div class="card-icon">🗡️</div>
      <div class="card-location">Black Leaf · Beat-Em-Up</div>
      <div class="card-title">Callen's Training</div>
      <div class="card-line"></div>
      <p class="card-desc">Train under Zachariel. Fight alongside Sylva. Two years of combat that will make Callen the deadliest person in any room. And then he'll learn what it was all for.</p>
      <div class="card-cta">Enter →</div>
    </a>

    <a class="game-card" href="mythanar-expanded/index.html" style="--delay: 2.45s">
      <div class="card-icon">🕳️</div>
      <div class="card-location">Blue River Village · Puzzle Dungeon</div>
      <div class="card-title">Mythanar's Cave</div>
      <div class="card-line"></div>
      <p class="card-desc">Five rooms. Five moral tests. The puzzle isn't solved by sacrifice — it's solved by refusing to sacrifice. The elves who built this failed their own test. Will you?</p>
      <div class="card-cta">Enter →</div>
    </a>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <a class="back-link" href="../index.html">Return to the Lore Navigator</a>
    <div class="footer-note">Kalmirth · Night Etdler</div>
  </footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>
